<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>UniConnect — Community</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css"/>
  <!-- Tailwind required for footer -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            navy: '#0d1b2a',
            'navy-mid': '#1a2e45',
            'navy-light': '#243b55',
            gold: '#c9a84c',
            'gold-light': '#e8c97a',
            cream: '#f5f0e8',
            'cream-dark': '#ede5d6',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            'serif': ['Playfair Display', 'serif'],
            'sans': ['DM Sans', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  <style>
    /* ── Topbar ── */

    /* ── Layout ── */
    .layout {
      display: flex;
      padding-top: var(--topbar-h);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }


    /* ── Main ── */
    .main {
      flex: 1;
      margin-left: var(--sidebar-w);
      padding: 2rem;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .course-column {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── Community Header ── */
    .course-header {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .course-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .course-instructor {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .course-description {
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ── Members Card ── */
    .members-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(13,27,42,0.07);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .members-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #9aaabb;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .members-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .member-avatar {
      width: 46px; height: 46px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      border: 2px solid #fff;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .member-avatar:nth-child(2) { background: var(--navy-mid); }
    .member-avatar:nth-child(3) { background: var(--navy-light); }
    .member-avatar:nth-child(4) { background: #2c4a6e; }
    .member-avatar:nth-child(5) { background: #1e3a52; }

    .members-overflow {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-left: 0.4rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      padding: 0;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .members-overflow:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }

    /* ── Modal ── */
    .modal-backdrop {
      display: none;
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(13,27,42,0.45);
      z-index: 200;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .modal-backdrop.open { display: flex; }

    .modal {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 480px;
      max-height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(13,27,42,0.18);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 1rem;
    }

    .modal-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .modal-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .modal-close {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: none;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }
    .modal-close:hover { background: var(--cream-dark); color: var(--navy); }

    .modal-body {
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .modal-student {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .modal-student:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .modal-avatar {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .modal-student-name {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    /* ── Feed Section ── */
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    /* ── Post Cards ── */
    .post-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(13,27,42,0.07);
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .post-actions {
      position: absolute;
      top: 1.25rem;
      right: 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .post-action-btn {
      width: 34px; height: 34px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--cream);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }
    .post-action-btn:hover { background: var(--cream-dark); color: var(--navy); }

    .post-author {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      padding-right: 8rem;
    }

    .post-avatar-initials {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .post-author-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem; }

    .post-author-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-dark); }
    .post-author-name a { color: var(--text-dark); text-decoration: none; }
    .post-author-name a:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

    .post-meta { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .post-meta a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; }
    .post-meta a:hover { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

    .post-community { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--navy); font-weight: 500; }
    .post-community a { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; }
    .post-community a:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

    .post-body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('header', { initials: 'LG' }) %>

  <div class="layout">

    <!-- Left Sidebar -->
    <%- include('sidebar', { activePage: 'communities' }) %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="main">
      <div class="course-column">

        <!-- Community Header -->
        <div class="course-header">
          <h1 class="course-title">Computer Science Club</h1>
          <p class="course-instructor">142 members · Founded 2018</p>
          <p class="course-description">
            A community for CS students to connect, collaborate, and grow. We host weekly talks, coding challenges, and networking events with industry professionals throughout the semester. Whether you're just getting started or already deep into your studies, there's a place for you here.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Members Card -->
        <div class="members-card">
          <div class="members-label">Members</div>
          <div class="members-row">
            <div class="member-avatar">JB</div>
            <div class="member-avatar">JS</div>
            <div class="member-avatar">LGR</div>
            <div class="member-avatar">AM</div>
            <div class="member-avatar">TR</div>
            <button class="members-overflow" onclick="document.getElementById('membersModal').classList.add('open')">… and 137 others.</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Community Feed -->
        <h2 class="section-title">Feed</h2>

        <!-- Post 1 -->
        <div class="post-card">
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Like">👍</button>
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Comment">💬</button>
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Bookmark">🔖</button>
          </div>
          <div class="post-author">
            <div class="post-avatar-initials">KP</div>
            <div class="post-author-info">
              <span class="post-author-name"><a href="profile.html">Keiko Park</a></span>
              <span class="post-meta"><a href="post.html">March 6, 2026 at 11:20 AM</a></span>
              <span class="post-community"><a href="community.html">Computer Science Club</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="post-body">
            <p>Hey everyone! Just a reminder that our speaker event this Thursday at 6 PM in EME 101 is still on. We have a senior engineer from Microsoft coming to talk about career paths in cloud infrastructure.</p>
            <p>Free pizza will be provided. Please RSVP in the form linked in the bio so we can get a headcount for food. Bring questions — she's happy to do a real Q&amp;A!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 2 -->
        <div class="post-card">
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Like">👍</button>
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Comment">💬</button>
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Bookmark">🔖</button>
          </div>
          <div class="post-author">
            <div class="post-avatar-initials">DN</div>
            <div class="post-author-info">
              <span class="post-author-name"><a href="profile.html">Diego Navarro</a></span>
              <span class="post-meta"><a href="post.html">March 5, 2026 at 3:45 PM</a></span>
              <span class="post-community"><a href="community.html">Computer Science Club</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="post-body">
            <p>Sharing my notes from last week's session on system design patterns — covered monoliths vs. microservices, event-driven architecture, and when to use each.</p>
            <p>Happy to discuss further or do a follow-up session if there's interest. Drop a 👍 if you'd find that useful and I'll set something up with the officers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 3 -->
        <div class="post-card">
          <div class="post-actions">
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Like">👍</button>
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Comment">💬</button>
            <button class="post-action-btn" title="Bookmark">🔖</button>
          </div>
          <div class="post-author">
            <div class="post-avatar-initials">JB</div>
            <div class="post-author-info">
              <span class="post-author-name"><a href="profile.html">Jaden Bryant</a></span>
              <span class="post-meta"><a href="post.html">March 4, 2026 at 9:05 PM</a></span>
              <span class="post-community"><a href="community.html">Computer Science Club</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="post-body">
            <p>Does anyone have experience with Rust? I've been wanting to try it for a side project and curious if anyone here has used it beyond a tutorial.</p>
            <p>Specifically interested in whether it's worth learning for systems work alongside C++ or if one replaces the other for most practical purposes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div><!-- /.course-column -->
    </main>

  </div><!-- /.layout -->

  <!-- Members Modal -->
  <div class="modal-backdrop" id="membersModal" onclick="if(event.target===this)this.classList.remove('open')">
    <div class="modal">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <span class="modal-title">Members — Computer Science Club</span>
        <button class="modal-close" onclick="document.getElementById('membersModal').classList.remove('open')">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="modal-student"><div class="modal-avatar">JB</div><span class="modal-student-name">Jaden Bryant</span></div>
